    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3 in a truly concours-ready state. This example features the legendary S54B32 power unit, delivering linear throttle response via six individual throttle bodies and a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. The chassis is structurally flawless with documented subframe reinforcement and a freshly serviced variable M-limited slip differential. Mechanically, the dual-VANOS system has been overhauled and rod bearings replaced as preventative maintenance, ensuring the high-revving valvetrain operates with factory-spec tolerances. Suspension geometry remains dialed with OEM bushings for communicative feedback. This is a turn-key specimen for the collector seeking peak mechanical harmony and uncompromised performance.",
